### Create a session
POST {{host}}/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetRole": ".NET Backend Junior"
}

### List my sessions
GET {{host}}/api/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reject request without a token (expect 401)
GET {{host}}/api/sessions

### Session that does not exist (expect 404)
GET {{host}}/api/sessions/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}